    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="writingSession" n="1">
                <pb n="1r"/>
                <p>
                    <note hand="#addressee" place="mTop">envoyer le pié de lunette zur
                            See<supplied cert="high">.</supplied>
                        <lb/>
                        <choice>
                            <orig>Ecrivez</orig>
                            <reg>Écrivez</reg>
                        </choice> si quelqu’un a vu <choice>
                            <orig>a</orig>
                            <reg>à</reg>
                        </choice>
                        <placeName ref="https://www.geonames.org/2988507">Paris</placeName>
                        <lb/>
                        <bibl corresp="https://edition-humboldt.de/v8/RIUKP4EA">
                            <choice>
                                <orig>le</orig>
                                <reg>les</reg>
                            </choice>
                            <choice>
                                <orig>Molecules</orig>
                                <reg>Molécules</reg>
                            </choice> de <persName ref="http://d-nb.info/gnd/118674455">Brown</persName>
                        </bibl> et ce que
                        l’on<lb/>en dit</note>
                </p>
                <p>Je Vous supplie cher <lb/>ami, de commander <lb/>chez <persName ref="http://d-nb.info/gnd/117659487">Chevalier</persName> un <lb/>
                    <hi rendition="#u">microscope</hi> semblable
                    <lb/>aux derniers qu’il <lb/>a <choice>
                        <sic>envoyé</sic>
                        <corr cert="high">envoyés</corr>
                    </choice> ici, mais <lb/>par la poste adressé <lb/>
                    <choice>
                        <orig>a</orig>
                        <reg>à</reg>
                    </choice>
                    <choice>
                        <abbr>Mr</abbr>
                        <expan>Monsieur</expan>
                    </choice>
                    <persName ref="http://d-nb.info/gnd/104268190">
                        <hi rendition="#u">Link</hi>
                    </persName>. <note hand="#author" place="left">
                        <hi rendition="#uu">
                            <persName ref="http://d-nb.info/gnd/104268190">Link</persName>
                        </hi>
                    </note> Faites <lb/>le payer <choice>
                        <orig>a</orig>
                        <reg>à</reg>
                    </choice>
                    <persName ref="http://d-nb.info/gnd/116918241">Leo</persName> mais <lb/>
                    <choice>
                        <sic>recommander</sic>
                        <corr cert="high">recommandez</corr>
                    </choice> qu’on se <lb/>presse et que la <lb/>construction <choice>
                        <orig>mecanique</orig>
                        <reg>mécanique</reg>
                    </choice>
                    <lb/>et l’emballage des <lb/>
                    <choice>
                        <orig>pieces</orig>
                        <reg>pièces</reg>
                    </choice> soyent moins <lb/>mauvaisses. Observez <lb/>l’effet de ma lettre
                    <lb/>sur <persName ref="http://d-nb.info/gnd/118779249">Legendre</persName>
                    <supplied cert="high">.</supplied> Je Vous <lb/>embrasse tendrement<supplied cert="high">.</supplied>
                </p>
               <closer>
                    <signed>Ht<pb n="1v"/>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
